    ('12', '27.7046702', '85.3424033' ,'Kathmandu Grill Restaurant & bar','This Kathmandu grill restaurant and wine bar garden was perfect. impressed and parking also huge campare to the  thamel area off course food and beverage also reasonable price kitchen and service (all the staff) service is great. 27.7185966 85.3078603 
