    ('27', '27.7094','85.52626' ,'CITY CENTER','Located centrally in the heart of Kathmandu in Kamal Pokhari, City Center is a shoppers delight.NLIC City Centre is Nepals first integrated family centre located at the heart of Kathmandu, comprising of five floors, full of clothing stores as well as food and entertainment facilities which adds a very blissful experience to the visitors. It is a centrally air conditioned mall, with CCTV, smoke detector, fire alarm, fire hydrant, sufficient power supply with 24 hours generator backup, lively open space at the exterior with a long footpath fitted with light poles, up- to date toiletries and toiled facilities for handicapped people. All shops have tempered glass to lubricate window-shopping. There is also accessibility to telephone line and broad band internet service in every shop.
