    ('29', '27.6772','85.3170' ,'LABIM MALL','Labim Mall spread over 200,000 square feet brings a world-class shopping experience to Nepal. With QFX cinemas, astonishing variety of cuisine and over 70 top notch brands, it captures the spirit and spacious street style of a global lifestyle with the charm and authentic spirit of Nepal. It is located in Pulchowk, Lalitpur, Nepal.

    Labim Mall is elegant by keeping modernity in mind and is also motivated by traditional Nepalese values of hospitality, kindness and reverence. You’ll experience a unique shopping delight at over 200, 000 square feet. Labim Mall finds shopping privileges for customers of 70 premium brands and a world of luxury accessories where their masterpieces are shown by cutting-edge brands. In addition, it also has a number of exciting locations that will keep you busy throughout your day!

