    ('32', '27.701195723333','85.319914360606' ,'KATHMANDU FUN PARK','Kathmandu Fun Park is the biggest amusement park in Nepal offering varieties of activities including car skating, Columbus, train, tower game, Ferris wheel, helicopter for kids, boat games, bungee for kids, and more that are best suited for children and youngsters.

    Kathmandu Fun Park is located in the heart of the city making it easily accessible from all parts of Kathmandu valley. The park offers group discounts except during the public holidays which are often busy with visitors.

