    ' ,'WHOOPEE LAND AMUSEMENT WATER PARK','Whoopee Land a modern amusement waterpark has come into operation in Chobhar, Kirtipur. The site is located 3.5 km from Balkhu. Innovation Pvt. Ltd. has invested 250 million rupees to bring this amusement park into operation. This park serves as a popular weekend getaway for people living in Kathmandu valley. This stunning fantasy world provides many facilities and places for children to enjoy activities such as slides, children’s playground,360 degrees Ranger, 180 degrees Frisbee, the bouncy Zorb ball along curvy meadows and Animatronics Dinosaurs. Non-stop aquatic thrill rides feature Multilane, high-Speed Slide, Family Raft, Space Bowl, Spectacular kids water-play fort Multipin Platform for kiddies. Aqua venture in the idyllic environment is perfect for all vacationers; thrill-seekers, and all age people. The water park offers an extreme level of excitement and delivers an “Aqua” Adventure unlike any other. Hold on as the Water Park slides takes your breath away at every turn, splash down on our slides. And don’t forget, The Bee Garden and dining area that can accommodate up to 200 guests for birthday parties, family reunions or any group outing.
